text: IF Rune is a sports club in Kungs√∂r, Sweden. It was established on 28 April 1908. The club runs gymnastics and orienteering. It earlier also ran bandy and soccer. The men's bandy team played in the Swedish top division in 1935. The men's soccer team played in the Swedish second division during the seasons of 1934-1935, 1936-1937 and 1937-1938. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1908 establishments in Sweden Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs
